commit message:
Change NFC subsystem to use nordpol

- Use the TagDispatcher to dispatch NFC events
- Use AndroidCard to get an IsoCard instead of an IsoDep
- Run UI changes in tagDiscovered on the UI thread since it is executed on a
background thread

Use nordpol 0.1.8

- This version fixes the default behavior that disables NFC sounds
Allow the app to be launched by default on URL for Android 6.0.
